		{"id":"2419a6554f7e930d","x":590,"y":753,"width":970,"height":647,"type":"text","text":"![[Pasted image 20241121142017.png]]\n\n设 $F(x)=\\int^{x}_{0}f(t)dt$, 于是有 $F(0)=F(\\pi)=0$.\n$$\n\\int^{\\pi}_{0}f(x)\\cos dx= \\int^{\\pi}_{0}\\cos x dF(x)=\\int^{\\pi}_{0}F(x)\\sin x dx\n$$\n使用开区间的积分中值定理推得 $\\xi \\in (0,\\pi),F(\\xi)=0$.\n故使用罗尔定理知 $f(\\xi_{1})=f(\\xi_{2})=0$.\n\n>[!note] 证明开区间的积分中值定理\n>假设 $f(x)$ 在 $[a,b]$ 连续, $(a,b)$ 可导. 设\n>$$\n>F(x)= \\int^{x}_{a}f(t)dt\n>$$\n>根据拉格朗日中值定理, 存在 $\\xi \\in(a,b)$, 有\n>$$\n>f(\\xi)=F(\\xi) = \\dfrac{F(b)-F(a)}{b-a}= \\dfrac{\\int^{b}_{a}f(t)dt}{b-a} \\implies \\int^{b}_{a}f(t)dt = f'(\\xi)(b-a)\n>$$\n\n\n\n"}
